Стеклянный цилиндрический сосуд без ручки, служащий для питья. 
"Выпить стакан чаю ."
(чаю: Some nouns have a second genitive form, also called partitive. It has limited usage: it’s only used when referring to a part of something (e.g. «чашка чаю» ‘a cup of tea’, but not «*вкус чаю» ‘taste of tea’). It only looks like dative. Most words either don’t have this form or sound colloquial with this form.)
